~ start
I saw a couple of slimy blobs roaming around. Thought they were harmless until I saw them eat out someone's foot. Luckily they're easy to kill. Some crazy ass bandits applied the slime material on their bullets, adds poison to it apparently (i learnt out the hard way).
I wish I had more to say, but really, I don't know much yet. After the final bombs fell on my shelter, I almost got killed by this dragon looking thing. It had hundreds of teeth and was flying. That's how I ended up here.
If I don't die here.. if I somehow escape this hell, maybe I'll tell you more about what happened.
=> END